title: Best of The SXSW Playlist, Part 4
description:
Part 4 of 6, from Lorrie Matheson to Portugal the Man. Best songs on here are The Job Song, Wake the Sun, and Bright Red Stone(Bright Red Stone is one of the best songs overall). Strangest thing on here is O&#039;Death, which has amazing instrumentals and the worst vocalist I heard through 758 songs(not counting Wing, which was just confusing. You&#039;ll get that later). Also, fair warning, there are a lot of mediocre vocals on here, and a lot of non-existant vocals on here.
